creator: Pi Apps Developer
descriptionHtml:
PiChat is a FREE messaging app. PiChat uses your phone's Internet connection to let you message and call friends and family members. Using PiChat you can send and receive messages, calls, photos, videos, documents, and Voice Messages.

PiChat uses your phone's Internet connection to let you message and call friends and family.

• MultiMedia Messages: Send and receive photos, videos, documents, and Voice Messages.

• Calls : Call your friends and family for free with PiChat Calling.

• Group Chat: Group chats with your friends or family.

Share your location, contacts , files and more!

*Data charges may apply. Contact your provider for details.
descriptionShort: PiChat is a FREE messaging app
title: PiChat

creator: Pi Apps Developer
descriptionHtml:
Swing: Say "hello" to the world. With a simple, secure and feature rich messenger

Experience a hassle free chat within your profession and personal contacts. crystal-clear voice calls beyond boundaries adds to the experience.. Group chat allows you to stay connected to your family, friends, and coworkers. Add a layer atop of text messaging and express a lot more with multimedia. Swing state-of-the-art end to end encryption lets you communicate and share moments without worrying about privacy and security. It doesn't follow you around with ads or store your activity. Therefore we have nothing to sell to advertisers that track you across the Internet.


Connect anywhere, anytime and on any device
Start a one to one conversation with your friend, colleague or a group chat with upto 256 people.

Lost for words? Bring your conversations to life
Say a lot more with photos, GIFs, stickers, location, videos, and including some ❤️✌️🤣


Keep the conversation going
Sync all of your chats from device to device, and stay in touch across Android, iOS, and the web
